<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Samuel Umtiti \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 chung k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Les Bleus. H\u00f2a chung ni\u1ec1m vui chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Descham, c\u00e1c C\u0110V t\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh nh\u01b0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9, khi Kh\u1ea3i Ho\u00e0n M\u00f4n ng\u1eadp tr\u00e0n s\u1eafc xanh \u0111\u1ecf - m\u00e0u c\u1edd c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. H\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t chi\u1ebfc xe c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1ecb ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp do qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi, c\u00f9ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u fan h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 tr\u00e8o l\u00ean n\u00f3c xe \u0111\u1ec3 ca h\u00e1t.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CDV Phap do ra duong an mung\" title=\"C\u0110V Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0103n m\u1eebng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/phap-vao-chung-ket-nguoi-dan-paris-do-ra-duong-di-bao.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u0110V Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0103n m\u1eebng sau khi \u0110T l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t di\u1ec5n ra kh\u1eafp n\u01a1i, d\u1ecdc con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u00e0 th\u1edd Notre Dame. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa th\u00f4i, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup sau trong 2 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7. V\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u00f2n vui m\u1eebng h\u01a1n l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u00f9ng xem nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh C\u0110V Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng<br />\r\n</strong> <br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/063835-1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://