>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-tiep-tuc-de-lai-hinh-anh-cuc-xau-vi-thoi-cau-gio-421-190900.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/mbappe-tiep-tuc-de-lai-hinh-anh-cuc-xau-vi-thoi-cau-gio.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-tiep-tuc-de-lai-hinh-anh-cuc-xau-vi-thoi-cau-gio-421-190900.html\">Sau tuy\u1ec7t chi\u00eau \u0103n v\u1ea1, Mbappe ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ef1c x\u1ea5u v\u00ec th\u00f3i c\u00e2u gi\u1edd</span><br />\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Kylian Mbappe b\u00e0y tr\u00f2 c\u00e2u gi\u1edd trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/Deschamps-phat-bieu-sau-tran-dau-Phap-1-0-Bi-ban-ket-World-Cup-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diem-nhan-phap-vs-bi-tran-cau-thuc-dung-421-190893.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng si\u00eau th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br />\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i. Sau c\u00f9ng, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/20180710T190939Z_500562221_UP1EE7A1H82S7_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPFRBE.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-bi-461-190890.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 (World Cup 2018)</span><br />\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Umtiti \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Les Bleus v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1116","checkdouble":"190905"},{"date":"06:51 11/07","title":"Thua tr\u1eadn, sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ph\u00e1p \u201cph\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CLB Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u201cph\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean ng\u00f4i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSu\u1ed1t k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup 2018 t\u1edbi nay, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y t\u00ednh th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p trong tay c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, HLV Didier Deschamps v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ph\u00e1p th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea7m ch\u1eebng, \u0111\u1eb7t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 n\u01a1i ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Antoine Griezmann hay Kylian Mbappe c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nhanh nh\u1eb9n, Les Blues ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Thibaut-Courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-Phap-1-0-Bi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi B\u1ec9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p l\u1ea1i t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. Trung v\u1ec7 Samuel Umtiti l\u00ean tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Griezmann gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 l\u1ee5c l\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2y, s\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 h\u01a1n. Sau c\u00f9ng, h\u1ecd khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c m\u0169i c\u00f4ng B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois b\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 26 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u201cph\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. \u201cPh\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1eed t\u1ebf\u201d, Courtois n\u00f3i v\u1edbi h\u00e3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Sporza c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Courtois\" title=\"thu mon Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/courtois-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ee9c x\u00fac</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cH\u1ecd c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n ch\u01a1i theo c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00f3 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. H\u1ecd ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThua tr\u1eadn, B\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a Courtois s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i thua trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft 2 gi\u1eefa Croatia v\u00e0 Anh v\u00e0o 21h ng\u00e0y 14/7 t\u1edbi. C\u00f2n Ph\u00e1p b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra 22h ng\u00e0y 15/7 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9 tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-vao-chung-ket-nguoi-dan-paris-do-ra-duong-di-bao-421-190905.html\">Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Paris \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i b\u00e3o</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hlv-deschamps-khen-pogba-sau-tran-thang-bi-469-190901.html\">HLV Deschamps khen Pogba sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/deschamps-phat-bieu-sau-tran-phap-10-bi-421-190897.html\">Ph\u00e1p l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup, Deschamps v\u1eabn k\u00e9m vui</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ferdinand-tron-mat-lam-the-quai-nao-do-duoc-mbappe-421-190894.html\">Ferdinand tr\u00f2n m\u1eaft: L\u00e0m th\u1ebf qu\u00e1i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mbappe?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-phap-10-bi-421-190892.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 1-0 B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1115","checkdouble":"190907"},{"date":"16:02 10/07","title":"Ronaldo s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Juventus?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/ronaldo-se-da-o-dau-trong-doi-hinh-juventus.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">4-3-1-2 v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/lo-so-ao-cua-ronaldo-o-juventus-180-190540.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span>, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gonzalo Higuain kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 31 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t vui v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh CR7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus Allegri c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus Allegri c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Cristiano-Ronaldo-toi-Juventus-Allegri-co-the-van-hanh-so-do-nao-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4-3-1-2 v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi n\u1ebfu Ronaldo h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u1edbi Higuain. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft nhau r\u1ea5t r\u00f5, h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i kho\u1ea3ng 80 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi nhau. Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain l\u00e0 2 trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, HLV Massimiliano Allegri ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng 4-3-1-2 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u1ede tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, Matuidi, Pjanic v\u00e0 Can l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng. Dybala ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng cho Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDybala l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00f4 h\u1ea1n, nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdc khe c\u1ee7a anh mang \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Dybala, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain s\u1ebd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat xa c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n hai ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u0169ng gi\u00fap anh ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>4-3-3 v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Ronaldo, Higuain v\u00e0 Dybala</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Allegri v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Higuain, Dybala v\u00e0 Mandzukic l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. Khi Mandzukic kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n th\u00ec Douglas Costa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4-3-3 voi bo ba tan cong Ronaldo, Higuain va Dybala\" title=\"4-3-3 v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Ronaldo, Higuain v\u00e0 Dybala\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/2.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4-3-3 v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Ronaldo, Higuain v\u00e0 Dybala</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 v\u1edbi 3 m\u0169i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng gi\u00fap Juventus mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u00e1t huy nhi\u1ec1u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng g\u1ed3m 3 m\u0169i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, Ronaldo, Higuain v\u00e0 Dybala s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean nhau. CR7 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, Dybala ch\u01a1i c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n c\u00f2n Higuain ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb h\u1ecd s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u1ee7ng&nbsp;khi\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, Juventus c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean gia l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 Pjanic, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng cho b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi Emre Can v\u00e0 Blaise Matuidi \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n, Juventus c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng khi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a 2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi Ronaldo \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed5 d\u1ed3n v\u00e0o CR7. Khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Higuain v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Juventus s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, khi \u0111\u00f3 anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4-2-3-1 voi Ronaldo da cao nhat tren hang cong\" title=\"4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi Ronaldo \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/3.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi Ronaldo \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Higuain r\u1eddi Juventus, HLV Allegri kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng b\u1edfi Ronaldo ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi CR7 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a Dybala t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau, Ronaldo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra t\u1edbi 18 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Higuain nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 2 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi Ronaldo thay v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Higuain, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Dybala \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. V\u1edbi Douglas Costa v\u00e0 Mario Mandzukic b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Dybala, Juventus s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng v\u0169 kh\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>4-3-3 v\u1edbi Dybala, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Douglas Costa tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Higuain r\u1eddi Juventus ho\u1eb7c HLV Allegri kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina, \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 v\u1edbi Paulo Dybala, Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Douglas Costa l\u00e0 3 m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4-3-3 voi Dybala, Ronaldo va Douglas Costa tren hang cong\" title=\"4-3-3 v\u1edbi Dybala, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Douglas Costa tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/4.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4-3-3 v\u1edbi Dybala, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Douglas Costa tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, Ronaldo s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong, Dybala v\u00e0 Douglas Costa ch\u01a1i \u1edf hai c\u00e1nh. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 CR7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 t\u1ed1t th\u00ec t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Dybala v\u00e0 Douglas Costa, s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa b\u1ed9 ba n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMiralem Pjanic s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng cho b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia c\u0169ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdc khe s\u1eafc l\u1eb9m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 thi\u00ean t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Juventus&nbsp;mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1114","checkdouble":"190857"},{"date":"16:21 10/07","title":"4 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-anh-se-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1eb1m \u1edf nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh, \u0110T Anh \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi s\u00e1t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup s\u1ebd quay v\u1ec1 Anh sau 52 n\u0103m.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup n\u0103m 1966, tuy nhi\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao vua \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng cao chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap. N\u0103m nay \u1edf v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5, Tam s\u01b0 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c b\u1edfi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Southgate sang Nga m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Anh v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chinh ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u b\u1edfi ngay c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Lampard, Gerrard, Ferdinand,\u2026 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 \u0111\u00f3. \u0110T Anh tham d\u1ef1 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, v\u00ec th\u1ebf h\u1ecd \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf S\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 tung h\u00f4 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u00edt ph\u1ea3i mang theo nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin \u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin \u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/4-ly-do-de-tin-DT-Anh-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018<span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, \" lucida=\"\" grande\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" start;\"=\"\">\u00a0l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra khi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c \u00e9p</span></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mang theo nh\u1eefng g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Ngay c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0 ieran Trippier, Jesse Lingard v\u00e0 John Stones c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u0103ng hoa. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o v\u00e0 to\u00e1t l\u00ean s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin khi m\u00e0 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap Tam s\u01b0 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Croatia v\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng th\u1ee9 N\u0103m t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00e1t danh hi\u1ec7u<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 EURO hay World Cup, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. V\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111ang mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 mang c\u00fap v\u00e0ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea3o qu\u1ed1c s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y tinh th\u1ea7n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Colombia thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 tinh qu\u00e1i. D\u00f9 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n song c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 khao kh\u00e1t gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m, qua \u0111\u00f3 ph\u00e1 lu\u00f4n l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed7i lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat 11m t\u1ea1i World Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia hay Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n cho th\u1ea5y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u00f4ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng mang t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 v\u0169 kh\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Anh vao ban ket World Cup 2018 day thuyet phuc.\" title=\"\u0110T Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/paul-scholes-pep-co-anh-huong-den-thanh-cong-cua-dt-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 truy\u1ec1n ki\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh nh\u01b0 Brazil, \u0110\u1ee9c, T\u00e2y Ban Nha,\u2026 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0m t\u0103ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Croatia v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p/B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ngang c\u01a1 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00ec th\u1ebf c\u0169ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u0129 nhi\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra ch\u1ee7 quan b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1nh \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. C\u00f3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady th\u00ec chuy\u1ec7n\u00a0\u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u vi\u1ec3n v\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\u2018G\u00e0 son\u2019 Harry Kane<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Harry Kane \u0111ang l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Anh tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga h\u00e8 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 Kane ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb ch\u00ea l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh, s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Tottenham th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane\" title=\"Harry Kane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/world-cup-khong-chi-la-qua-bong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Harry Kane l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c danh hi\u1ec7u World Cup</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 b\u00e0n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i th\u00ec c\u00f3 2 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Tunisia, c\u00f9ng 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng r\u1ea5t may m\u1eafn khi b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m ch\u00e2n Kane\u00a0t\u1eeb\u00a0c\u00fa s\u00fat xa c\u1ee7a Ruben Loftus-Cheek. N\u00f3i n\u00f4m na, Kane \u0111\u00e3 hay l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n... may. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00edt th\u1edf b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed \u1edf ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, Harry Kane \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00e1c v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2u anh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 chung k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n v\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-dai-chien-nguoi-croatia-lay-messi-ra-doa-tuyen-anh-421-190735.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/truoc-dai-chien-nguoi-croatia-lay-messi-ra-doa-tuyen-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-dai-chien-nguoi-croatia-lay-messi-ra-doa-tuyen-anh-421-190735.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia l\u1ea5y Messi ra d\u1ecda tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span><br>\r\nCroatia chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Tam S\u01b0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Dalic \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0110T Anh b\u1eb1ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft Harry Kane.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh-421-190780.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh-421-190780.html\">HLV Croatia \u0111\u1ec1 cao Sterling tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh, HLV Croatia, Zlatko Dalic \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Raheem Sterling, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tam...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/mandzukic-canh-bao-dt-anh-truoc-dai-chien-469-190794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/mandzukic-canh-bao-dt-anh-truoc-dai-chien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/mandzukic-canh-bao-dt-anh-truoc-dai-chien-469-190794.html\">Mandzukic c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mario Mandzukic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-xu-angle-phu-bong-len-lich-su-466-190667.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-xu-angle-phu-bong-len-lich-su.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-xu-angle-phu-bong-len-lich-su-466-190667.html\">\u0110T Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: Khi x\u1ee9 \u0102ng-l\u00ea ph\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng l\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span><br>\r\nMang b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 - \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay \u0111ang ph\u1ee7...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1113","checkdouble":"190858"},{"date":"16:31 10/07","title":"Sterling \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup\u2026 tuy\u1ec7t hay","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/sterling-dang-co-mot-ky-world-cup-tuyet-hay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Wayne Rooney v\u1eeba m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i DC United. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Rooney \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Anh khi \u0111ang chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2>Rooney ch\u00fac Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a G\u00e3 Shrek thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i MLS \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eaft b\u0103ng kh\u00e1nh th\u00e0nh SV\u0110 Audi Field, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. Tranh th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u r\u1ea5t l\u1ea1c quan.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi&rdquo; &ndash; Rooney cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang mong ch\u1edd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0, c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng t\u1ec9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo d\u00f5i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 HLV Gareth Southgate, t\u00f4i ch\u00fac h\u1ecd may m\u1eafn. H\u1ecd \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o. Hy v\u1ecdng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eefa v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, \u0111em c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rooney \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Anh trong ng\u00e0y kh\u00e1nh th\u00e0nh SV\u0110 c\u1ee7a DC United\" title=\"Rooney \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/rooney-chuc-dan-em-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rooney \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Anh trong ng\u00e0y kh\u00e1nh th\u00e0nh SV\u0110 c\u1ee7a DC United</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec3n Anh c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i DC United. Wayne Rooney cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y x\u1ecf gi\u00e0y ra s\u00e2n, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mong ch\u1edd \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0o ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o qu\u00ean.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap CLB gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, v\u00e0 \u0111em l\u1ea1i danh hi\u1ec7u cho SV\u0110 m\u1edbi khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam mai, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Gareth Southgate s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Croatia. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi Rooney \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Anh, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mong ch\u1edd h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-la-niem-cam-hung-cho-tre-em-beo-phi-421-190860.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/harry-kane-la-niem-cam-hung-cho-tre-em-beo-phi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-la-niem-cam-hung-cho-tre-em-beo-phi-421-190860.html\">Harry Kane l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho&hellip; tr\u1ebb em b\u00e9o ph\u00ec</span><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u01a1 s\u1edf chuy\u00ean v\u1ec1 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u1ea5y Kane l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho tr\u1ebb em...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sterling-dang-co-mot-ky-world-cup-tuyet-hay-421-190859.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/sterling-dang-co-mot-ky-world-cup-tuyet-hay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sterling-dang-co-mot-ky-world-cup-tuyet-hay-421-190859.html\">Sterling \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup&hellip; tuy\u1ec7t hay</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eric Dier l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1n b\u00e3o ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-anh-se-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-190858.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-anh-se-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-anh-se-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-190858.html\">4 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nN\u1eb1m \u1edf nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh, \u0110T Anh \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi s\u00e1t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1112","checkdouble":"190859"},{"date":"16:31 10/07","title":"Harry Kane l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho\u2026 tr\u1ebb em b\u00e9o ph\u00ec","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/harry-kane-la-niem-cam-hung-cho-tre-em-beo-phi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u01a1 s\u1edf chuy\u00ean v\u1ec1 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u1ea5y Kane l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho tr\u1ebb em b\u00e9o ph\u00ec.\r\n</h2><h2>Harry Kane &ldquo;t\u1eeb v\u1ecbt h\u00f3a thi\u00ean nga&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Tottenham l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Trong n\u0103m d\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ecbch 2017, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Harry Kane th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat kh\u00e9t ti\u1ebfng nh\u01b0 Cris Ronaldo, Leo Messi v\u00e0 Edinson Cavani.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Kane \u0111ang s\u1eafm vai tr\u00f2 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, v\u00e0 \u0111ang tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a Tam S\u01b0 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1eebng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5. Theo \u0111\u00f3, anh t\u1eebng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u1edfi tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean Arsenal, b\u1edfi th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh b\u1ee5 b\u1eabm c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi c\u00f2n nh\u1ecf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kane l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho tr\u1ebb em b\u00e9o ph\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kane l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho tr\u1ebb em b\u00e9o ph\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Kane-la-niem-cam-hung-cho-tre-em-beo-phi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kane l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho tr\u1ebb em b\u00e9o ph\u00ec</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 b\u1ecb b\u00e9o ph\u00ec, tr\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t m\u1eadp m\u1ea1p, x\u01b0\u01a1ng to v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Arsenal t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y trong h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n. Kane kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng m\u1ed9t v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean th\u1ec3 thao l\u1eafm, nh\u01b0ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m&rdquo; &ndash; Liam Brady, tr\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Arsenal chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Harry Kane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb b\u1ecb th\u1eeba c\u00e2n. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup, anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 v\u00ed d\u1ee5 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb \u0111ang b\u1ecb ch\u1ecdc gh\u1eb9o v\u00ec b\u00e9o ph\u00ec, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u tr\u00eau \u0111\u00f9a ki\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 &ldquo;b\u1ecdn m\u1eadp tr\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t ngu ng\u1ed1c&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 s\u1edf dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111ang l\u1ea5y Kane l\u00e0m h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh m\u1ed9t ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd h\u01a1n. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00f4, c\u1eadu b\u00e9 \u0111ang b\u1ecb b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 nh\u1ea1o b\u00e1ng v\u00ec th\u1eeba c\u00e2n, ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i theo con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec3n Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-dai-chien-nguoi-croatia-lay-messi-ra-doa-tuyen-anh-421-190735.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/truoc-dai-chien-nguoi-croatia-lay-messi-ra-doa-tuyen-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-dai-chien-nguoi-croatia-lay-messi-ra-doa-tuyen-anh-421-190735.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia l\u1ea5y Messi ra d\u1ecda tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span><br>\r\nCroatia chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Tam S\u01b0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Dalic \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0110T Anh b\u1eb1ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft Harry Kane.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-anh-se-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-190858.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-anh-se-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-ly-do-de-tin-dt-anh-se-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-190858.html\">4 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nN\u1eb1m \u1edf nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh, \u0110T Anh \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi s\u00e1t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1111","checkdouble":"190860"},{"date":"16:50 10/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u00f4i s\u1ee5c cho \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/nhung-du-doan-phap-vs-bi-va-nhan-dinh-soi-keo-phan-tich-ty-le-bi-vs-phap.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u00e0 c\u00e2n t\u00e0i c\u00e2n s\u1ee9c. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00fang ta ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</h2><br>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Ph\u00e1p th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi gian: 1h ng\u00e0y 11/7<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: S\u00e2n Saint-Petersburg<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: Ph\u00e1p -0.91*0:1/4*0.86 B\u1ec9<br>\r\nTBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: Nhi\u1ec1u -0.92*2 1/2*0.85 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh, soi k\u00e8o, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 k\u00e8o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh, soi k\u00e8o, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 k\u00e8o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/nhung-du-doan-phap-vs-bi-va-nhan-dinh-soi-keo-phan-tich-ty-le-bi-vs-phap.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 1h ng\u00e0y 1/7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n\u0110T Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Kylian Mbappe v\u00e0 Antoine Griezmann. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p khi ghi t\u1edbi 6 trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 9 b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng l\u1eaft l\u00e9o c\u1ee7a Mbappe v\u00e0 Griezmann gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 san b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKylian Mbappe ra m\u1eaft \u0110T Ph\u00e1p n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u00e0 k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 19 tr\u1eadn, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i PSG, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 l\u1ee5c l\u0103ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0110TQG tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe\" title=\"Mbappe\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Daniel-van-Buyten-phat-bieu-ve-Kylian-Mbappe-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mbappe \u0111ang t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhanh ch\u00f3ng, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 x\u00f3a tan nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c. Anh ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t ghi b\u00e0n cho \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup. Ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, Mbappe ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Pele, m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tu\u1ed5i teen ghi 2 b\u00e0n 1 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i World Cup. T\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng, t\u1edbi nay Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng cho Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng l\u1eeba b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n khi\u1ebfn ph\u00eda b\u00ean kia ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Ronaldo &ndash; Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u00e0i h\u00e0nh tinh m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi. D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-la-su-ket-hop-cua-ro-beo-henry-va-cristiano-421-190820.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/mbappe-la-su-ket-hop-cua-ro-beo-henry-va-cristiano.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-la-su-ket-hop-cua-ro-beo-henry-va-cristiano-421-190820.html\">Mbappe l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a R\u00f4 b\u00e9o, Henry v\u00e0 Cristiano</span><br>\r\n<span>Daniel van Buyten ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kylian Mbappe, c\u1ef1u sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 pha tr\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo Brazil, Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 Thierry...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Griezmann, th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 ra anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i hy sinh nhi\u1ec1u cho tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. \u0110\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Griezmann v\u00e0 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo k\u00e8m s\u00e1t sao. V\u00ec v\u1eady, ng\u00f4i sao thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Atletico Madrid bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u00f9i s\u00e2u t\u00ecm b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho \u0111\u00e0n em Mbappe.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, Griezmann c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay. C\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Giroud v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00eda sau c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba, Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t v\u0169 kh\u00ed l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i. Nh\u1eefng Ousmane Dembele, Nabil Fekir, Thomas Lemar, Florian Thauvin&hellip; b\u1eb1ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu \u00edch cho Les Bleus v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd an t\u00e2m v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Varane ghi ban cho Phap\" title=\"Varane ghi ban cho Phap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/4-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-20-cua-phap-truoc-uruguay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ph\u00e1p s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T B\u1ec9 s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup 2018, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec1u nghi ng\u1edd. Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama, t\u1edbi nay h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf 4 trong 5 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. Trong \u0111\u00f3, Tunisia, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Brazil \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf 2 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, nh\u01b0ng hai c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ee9ng. Tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1ng lo h\u01a1n khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Thomas Meunier b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 do nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 thay h\u1ecd d\u00f9 l\u00e0 Nacer Chadli hay Dedryck Boyata c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f2n tr\u00e1i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hau ve Meunier\" title=\"hau ve Meunier\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/hau-ve-Meunier.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Meunier b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7i lo cho B\u1ec9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 hai c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1. Nh\u1eefng Griezmann v\u00e0 Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch. H\u1ecd c\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Lucas Hern\u00e1ndez v\u00e0 Benjamin Pavard \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb1ng sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i l\u1ea5y c\u00f4ng b\u00f9 th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 14 b\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 sau 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, t\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh g\u1ea7n 3 b\u00e0n/ tr\u1eadn. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 Griezmann v\u00e0 Mbappe th\u00ec B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 Eden Hazard v\u00e0 De Bruyne l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng. V\u1edbi Lukaku th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 3 m\u0169i c\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, B\u1ec9 c\u00f2n nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi lot vao ban ket World Cup\" title=\"Bi lot vao ban ket World Cup\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Edwin-Van-der-Sar-du-doan-Bi-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y c\u00f4ng b\u00f9 th\u1ee7</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>G\u00f3c soi k\u00e8o Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 quy t\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean khi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9. Vi\u1ec7c gi\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a m\u1ed1c 2,25 b\u00e0n cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn. H\u1ecd \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i s\u1eeda sai t\u1eebng gi\u1edd t\u1eebng ph\u00fat v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c k\u00edch &ldquo;m\u1ed1c \u0111inh&rdquo; l\u00ean 2,5 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea9n tr\u1ecdng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m lu\u1eadt. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh m\u1ecfi tay d\u1ef1a theo xu h\u01b0\u1edbng r\u00f5 m\u1ed3n m\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nay. M\u1ed1c 2 b\u00e0n ch\u1eb5n \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y xu\u1ed1ng cu\u1ed1i. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 Bongda24h.vn d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, m\u1ed1c 2,75 t\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi s\u00e1t tr\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean ngang h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed1c 2,5 b\u00e0n hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh tr\u00ean c\u00e0ng gi\u00fap nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p c\u00f3 th\u00eam ni\u1ec1m tin. Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u1ea7y ni\u1ec1m vui l\u00e0 k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n vi\u00ean m\u00e3n v\u1edbi ch\u00fang ta.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Ph\u00e1p th\u1eafng 2-1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c</strong><br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 9 (U 9 1/2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 t\u1eeb h\u00f2a t\u1edbi h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 t\u1eeb h\u00f2a t\u1edbi h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 4 (U 4)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 t\u1eeb h\u00f2a t\u1edbi h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1110","checkdouble":"190861"}]}